nodes.text: Landez was a male who served in the Republic Military during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. Stationed aboard the space station Carrick Station, Landez held the rank of general.
Landez first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Galactic Strongholds, a expansion for Star Wars: The Old Republic released by BioWare in 2014, as a planetary conquest vendor.
